tps:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-6Az","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":43555,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/04\/21\/polygyny-warning\/","url_meta":{"origin":25331,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Polygamy: Warning against injustice to multiple wives","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 21, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever has two wives and he inclines to one of them over the other, he will come on the Day of Resurrection with one of his sides collapsed.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 4207 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25785,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/21\/shafiee-advice-private\/","url_meta":{"origin":25331,"position":1},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Nasihah: Sincere advice is given in private, not public","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 21, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Muzanni reported: Imam al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhoever admonishes his brother in private has been sincere to him and protected his reputation. Whoever admonishes him in public has humiliated him and betrayed him.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304\u2019 9\/140 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0632\u064e\u0646\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0641\u0650\u0639\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0638\u064e \u0623\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0627\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26826,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/10\/14\/shafii-arguing-deen-hate\/","url_meta":{"origin":25331,"position":2},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Debates: Arguing in religion breeds hate, bad will","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Rabia\u2019 ibn Sulayman reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cArguing about the religion hardens the heart and produces resentment.\u201d And Al-Shafi'i said, \"I never debated anyone but with sincere good will.\" Source: Siyar A'la\u0304m al-Nubala\u0304' 10\/28 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0639 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0633\u064f\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0641\u0650\u0639\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064f \u0641\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u0650\u064a\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27542,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/13\/best-answer-fool-silence\/","url_meta":{"origin":25331,"position":3},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Debate: Best answer to a fool is silence","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Imam al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah be pleased with him, said in his poetry, \u201cIf a fool speaks to you, do not answer him, for the best answer is silence. If you speak to him, you have delighted him. If you leave him, he nearly dies in anguish.\u201d Source: Di\u0304wa\u0304n al-Ima\u0304m al-Sha\u0304fi\u2019i\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33953,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/27\/shafii-malice-forgiveness\/","url_meta":{"origin":25331,"position":4},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Malice: Forgiveness relieved my soul of anxiety","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, wrote in his poetry, \u201cWhen I forgave and stopped holding malice against anyone, I relieved my soul of the worries of enmity.\u201d Source: Di\u0304wa\u0304n al-Sha\u0304fi\u02bbi\u0304 31 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0627\u0641\u0639\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0641\u064a \u0634\u0639\u0631\u0647 \u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0641\u064e\u0648\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0645\u0652 \u0623\u062d\u0652\u0642\u0650\u062f\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0623\u062d\u064e\u062f\u064d \u0623\u0631\u062d\u062a\u064f \u0646\u0641\u0633\u064a \u0645\u0646 \u0647\u0645\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0639\u062f\u0627\u0648\u0627\u062a\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26866,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/11\/17\/shafii-desire-no-praise\/","url_meta":{"origin":25331,"position":5},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Knowledge: I desire no praise or credit for teaching","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 17, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Hatim reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI never debated anyone and loved for him to be wrong. There is no knowledge in my heart but that I wish everyone could have it and attribute none of it to me.\u201d Source: A\u0304da\u0304b al-Sha\u0304fi\u2019i\u0304 wa Mana\u0304qibuh\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25331","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=25331"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25331\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=25331"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadith